snippet.title: Natsumiii - Retweets
snippet.description:
My first original song. Lyrics that I deeply relate to and hope that it resonates with everyone from this day and age. Stay strong, everyone! Much love. Hope you enjoy it!


This song is DMCA FREE :) 

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/51fPfYJNzWO1HgpIF0Ds90?si=oLJbbhR_SYCsN1SasGsdoA&utm_source=copy-link
